            Celebrity Status Accelerator Workshop
          </h4>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-2">
            Coming Q1 2026
          </p>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-4">
            Intensive personal branding transformation for entrepreneurs.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block mt-4 text-orange-500 font-semibold hover:text-orange-600">
            Get Notified →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-neutral-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200 mb-4">
        Want to Book Omar for Your Event?
      </h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-6">
        Speaking engagements, workshops, and private consulting available.
      </p>
      <a 
        href="/contact" 
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-500 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white hover:bg-orange-600 transition-colors"
      >
        Contact for Booking
      </a>
    </div>

